# isDefaultProfile

**Instance Property**

A Boolean value indicating whether to make the profile the default profile.

## Declaration

```swift
var isDefaultProfile: Bool? { get }
```

## Discussion

When the value in this property is [doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/Swift/true], the user wants to make the profile the default profile for the vehicle.

## Getting the Profile Information

- **profileName**: The name assigned to the profile.
- **profileNumber**: The profile index from which to restore the settings.
- **profileLabel**: The name assigned to the profile.
